
# NordFork

  A gnome shell theme

* Original Author : http://0rax0.deviantart.com/
*  Original Theme : http://0rax0.deviantart.com/art/GNOME-Shell-Nord-214295138

## Requirements

* git
	To download this project.
	
* Droid Sans
	To display as intended by the original author.

* Gnome Shell Tweak Tool
	To select and enable this theme

## Installation

1. mkdir ~/.themes
2. cd ~/.themes
3. git clone git://github.com/airtonix/gnome-shell-theme-nord.git ./nord
4. Open gnome-tweak-tool
5. Select the theme
6. alt+f2
7. r [enter]
